My part in the
journey is now over.

266
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:30,671
Hikaru, this is it.

267
00:19:30,705 --> 00:19:33,341
Hikaru?

268
00:19:33,374 --> 00:19:35,476
Hikaru?

269
00:19:35,510 --> 00:19:40,715
Oh, can you hear me?

270
00:19:40,715 --> 00:19:44,285
Hikaru, It was fun
being with you.

271
00:19:55,463 --> 00:19:56,831
HIKARU (VOICEOVER):
It's your turn.

272
00:19:56,864 --> 00:19:59,834
What are you waiting for?

273
00:19:59,867 --> 00:20:02,737
Hm?

274
00:20:02,737 --> 00:20:04,238
I said it's your turn.

275
00:20:07,108 --> 00:20:08,010
Sai?

276
00:20:32,300 --> 00:20:33,661
Sai?

